OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFirst Scottish city to ban 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpavement parking           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Edinburgh is set to become the first   
OL,6, city in Scotland to completely ban cars
OL,7, from parking on the pavement.          
OL,9,FUnder plans drawn up by the city       
OL,10,Fcouncil, drivers who mount the kerb    
OL,11,Fwill face a #100 fine.                 
OL,13,FDouble parking and parking at dropped  
OL,14,Fkerbs will also be banned - although   
OL,15,Fthere will be an exemption for delivery
OL,16,Fdrivers.                               
OL,18,FNational regulations will come into    
OL,19,Fforce on 11 December, with Edinburgh's 
OL,20,Fenforcement to start in January 2024.  
